Date: Fri, 20 Mar 2026 11:14:25 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: replace visual label designer with simple PRN editor

- Removed complex drag-and-drop visual designer (600+ lines)
- Replaced with clean PRN program text editor
- Shows all available placeholders: barcode, itemName, mrp, sellingPrice, hsnCode, size, sizeCode, cost
- Shows EPL2 example program for reference
- Loads existing saved template on open
- Save/set as default still works
- Generate PRN button downloads .PRN file directly
